{
  "stem": "20580.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I said to mommy, feel-- feel not-- because I'm not healthy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "A young guy, 20-some years.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This was the doctor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I was in-- in-- 19-- '32, I exactly remember the date.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- and I-- I came home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then my mother and the cousins, the mother Schechter, advised me, if you finish yeshiva and it's cost you a lot of money, you finish, you couldn't get work because you haven't got the privilege, you haven't got practice, you have to get [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH], a working card from the government.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I wrote to Pilsudski, and as I said before, he send me a card.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he send me a card.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I have the card.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I kept the card all the time with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] That was this place, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They call it [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In Polish, it's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is the head from the card, which I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Know what else you would know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, we're talking about Hitler's rise to power?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No This was in 1932--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--and '33.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back to Offenbach.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Offenbach is the main factory there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the 1933, we start to feel there an uncomfortable.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went back down there-- and I mean, I didn't-- couldn't-- couldn't stay there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Jews run away to America here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Try to run away from all over.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Why should I stay there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then I didn't continue-- I didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "About school, I know very little about chemistry, about the [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH] I know a little bit.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But, when Hitler come, later on, I start to work in the primitive style, which I was a good [NON-ENGLISH], they call it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Skinning it-- splitting the-- splitting-- the machine doesn't go it.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
